changeSet.comment: Adds a reference to the original transaction.
changeSet.sql: alter table transaction add column original_identifier varchar(255) null; comment on column "transaction"."original_identifier" is 'The identifier of the original transaction, in case of reversals.';

rollback.sql: alter table transaction drop column original_identifier;
